text: Abryutinskie Vyselki () is a rural locality (a village) in Yekimovskoye Rural Settlement of Ryazansky District, Ryazan Oblast, Russia. The population was 4 as of 2010. == Geography == The village is located 16 km south-west from Ryazan. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ryazan Oblast
title: Abryutinskie Vyselki
